- all services: a9s Dashboard: Requests to non-existing pages now properly
  renders a 404 page, even after refresh.
- all services: a9s Dashboard: Fixes a bug where the cards or part of it could
  go on top of the navbar.
- a9s-pg: Fixed postgresql-backup-endpoint to work with the newest a9s Backup Manager.
- a9s-pg: Added missing credentials to the a9s-pg Backup Agent.
- all services: SPI: Accept also single syslog and graphite endpoint.
- all services: a9s Dashboard: There is no error message popping up anymore if there is no backup
  for a service created yet.
- a9s PostgreSQL: single plans: Do not show `repmgr` PID file issues in the
  logs since it's a single plan that doesn't run `repmgr`.
- all services: a9s Dashboard: Fix an issue when open 2 different Service
