- a9s Backup Manager: Fix CVE-2019-5477 by updating the nokogiri gem.
- all services: a9s BOSH Deployer: Fix CVE-2019-5477 by updating the nokogiri
  gem.
- all services: a9s Backup Agent: Fix CVE-2019-5477 by updating the nokogiri
  gem.
- a9s-pg: Fix CVE-2019-5477 by updating the nokogiri gem.
- all services: a9s Dashboard: Fix CVE GHSA-3gx7-xhv7-5mx3 by updating
  eslint-utils.
- all services: a9s Dashboard: Fix Updates Tab in the a9s Dashboard when
  disabling the automatic updates.
- all services: a9s Service Broker: Fix CVE-2019-5477 by updating the nokogiri
  gem and Ruby to v2.6.3.
- a9s Service Guard: Fix CVE-2019-5477 by updating the nokogiri
  gem and Ruby to v2.6.3.
- all services: a9s Service Broker: Fix state of service instances when the
  update is not allowed.

***Added***

- all services: Add an Ops file that adds additional information as VM tags to
  each service instance,.
