- a9s PostgreSQL: PostgreSQL 9.4: Adds timestamps to logs for improved readability
- all services: a9s Dashboard: add documentation about the error codes caught
  by the NGINX and replaced with special pages.
- a9s Backup Manager: Adds an Index endpoint that returns information about the
  instances from all a9s Service Brokers known by the a9s Backup Manager.
- all services: a9s Dashboard: Adds a tooltip to the Backup duration column that
  explains what the spent time comes from.
- a9s Router: Documentation on required IaaS variable in order to deploy a9s Router.

***Updated***

- all services: a9s Backup Agent: Use metadata file on Azure.
- Stemcell: Update to BOSH stemcell version 456.x.
- Make service manifests and Ops files compliant to BOSH Director v270.0 and higher.
- a9s Elasticsearch: Elasticsearch 6.8.3

